summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from C. E. Remsberg and Belle F. Remsberg, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 7th day of March, 1907, to the North one-half (1/2) of Block Eleven (11) of Francis R. Day's La Grande Addition to the City of Seattle, being Lots One (1), Two (2), Three (3), Four (4), Five (5), Sixteen (16), Seventeen (17), Eighteen (18), Nineteen (19) and Twenty (20) of said Block Eleven (11).
